<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَتَى»</span> يَعْنِي مِنْ ,<span class="c5"> لُغَةِ هُذَيْلٍ قَالَ سَاعِدَةُ بْنُ جُؤَيَّةَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[البحر البسيط]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَا صِوَارًا مُدَرَّاةً مَنَاسِجُهَا ... مِثْلُ الْفِرِنْدِ إِذَا يَجْرِي مَتَى النُّظُمِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الطويل]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>بِوَادٍ يَمَانٍ يُنْبِتُ الشَّثَّ صَدْرُهُ ... وَأَسْفَلُهُ بِالْمَرَاجِلِ وَالشَّبَهَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الكامل]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ضَمِنَتْ بِرِزْقِ عِيَالِنَا أَرْمَاحُنَا ... مِلْءَ الْمَرَاجِلِ وَالصَّرِيحَ الْأَجْرَدَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ حَاتِمٌ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[البحر المنسرح]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَسُقِيتُ بِمَاءِ النَّمِيرِ، وَلَمْ ... أَتْرُكِ الْأُطْمَ جَمَّةَ الْحُفَرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">«مِنْ سِوَى أَنْفُسِهِمْ»</span> ،<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> مِنْ غَيْرِ أَهْلِ دِينِهِمْ <span class="c2">«فَيَسْتَبِيحَ بَيْضَتَهُمْ»</span> ، فَيَأْتِي عَلَى أَصْلِهِمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>